name: Switpina
description: Sure that it is hard to find a person who love the life more than me! I am a very optimistic person and sure that it is amazing, incredible, unbelievable! I am funny, interesting, positive and easy-going lady and you will never be bored with me. From the other side I am very tender, romantic and loving. I am very persistant in reaching my goals and have a strong character, but I am weak and delicate as every woman and here I am looking for a man who will be my strong shoulder and my everything.For my beloved one I am ready to do everything, and here I am looking for such man. I do not need Prince Charming, but I would like my man to be honest, sincere and reliable. I would like him to have a light character and be understanding and supportive.
